## 5. Jenkins Job Bana

Browser:

```
http://localhost:8080
```

### New Item

```
Lab8
```

Select:

```
Freestyle Project
```

---

## 6. Build Step Add Kar

Build Section:

```
Execute Windows Batch Command
```

Command:

```bat
cd /d C:\Users\YourName\IdeaProjects\Lab8

mvn clean test
```

Save.

---

## 7. Build Now

Click:

```
Build Now
```

Console Output me:

```
BUILD SUCCESS
```

Screenshot le.

---

## 8. Ansible Install (Ubuntu)

```bash
sudo apt update

sudo apt install ansible maven -y
```

Check:

```bash
ansible --version

mvn -version
```

---

## 9. deploy.yml

Project folder me:

```yaml
---
- name: Run Maven Project
  hosts: localhost
  connection: local

  tasks:

    - name: Build Project
      command: mvn clean install
      args:
        chdir: /mnt/c/Users/YourName/IdeaProjects/Lab8
```

---

## 10. Run Ansible

```bash
ansible-playbook deploy.yml
```

Output:

```text
PLAY RECAP

localhost : ok=1 changed=1 failed=0
```

Screenshot le.

